name: Still Life 7.0
description:
Fizz Pop (b.1974)  
2010  
12000 x 9600 pixels  
Source: Rachel Ruysch, Still Life with Flowers on a Marble Tabletop, 1716, oil on canvas, 48.5 cm x 39.5 cm  

  In 2010 this digital painting was released as a limited edition cibachrome print in two sizes; an edition of 7, 30” X 24” & an edition of 21, 14" X 11”.  Before the cibachrome print was discontinued, all the smaller editions were produced, but only one from the larger edition.
